notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: Chao Yang, Jiong Chun, Balian Zhong and Xuzhong Luo contributed to the conception and design of the study and data analysis; Hongli Chen and Jiong Chun collected the plant material and performed molecular distillation and GC-MS analysis; Chao Yang and Hui Chen carried out the antioxidant, MTT, apoptosis experiments and data analysis; Chao Yang and Jiong Chun wrote the manuscript. All authors reviewed and approved the manuscript.
